BATCH TRANSCRIPTION CREATE

  The `spx batch transcription create` command creates new
  requests to transcribe remote audio streams.

USAGE: spx batch transcription create [...]

  CONNECTION                      (see: spx help batch connection)
    --key KEY                     (see: spx help batch key)
    --region REGION               (see: spx help batch region)

  CREATE
    --name NAME                   (see: spx help batch transcription name)
    --model URL                   (see: spx help batch transcription create model)
    --content URL                 (see: spx help batch transcription create content)
    --content @URLs.txt           (see: spx help batch transcription create content)
    --language LANGUAGE           (see: spx help batch transcription create language)

  PARALLEL PROCESSING
    --threads NUMBER              (see: spx help batch threads)
    --processes NUMBER            (see: spx help batch processes)

  ADVANCED
    --project URL                 (see: spx help batch transcription project)
    --wait [TIMEOUT]              (see: spx help batch transcription wait)

